overview: May 5th, 2012 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Cinco De Mayo from the Bloomington National Guard Armory in Bloomington, Indiana, USA. Matches include:  • CZW World Heavyweight Title Match MASADA (c) vs. Michael Elgin  • CZW Junior Heavyweight Title Best Two Out Of Three Falls Match Sami Callihan (c) vs. Drake Younger  • Hy-Zaya vs. Kyle Maverick  • Remi Wilkins & Trevor Court vs. D-N-A (Aaron McCormick & Doug Charlez) vs. American Wrestling Warriors (Jeff Halloway & Troy Marcum) vs. The Northern Fight Club (Brent Banks & Sebastian Suave)  • Alex Colon vs. AR Fox  • Jake Crist vs. Adam Cole  • BJ Whitmer vs. DJ Hyde  • Barbed Wire Boards Match Danny Havoc vs. Ron Mathis  • CZW Wired TV Title Match Dave Crist (c) vs. Devon Moore
title: CZW Cinco De Mayo
